===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{lb|en|obsolete}} The act of [[restrain]]ing oneself. {{defdate|Attested from the early 16<sup>th</sup> century until the med 17<sup>th</sup> century.}}
# The act of [[abstain]]ing or [[refrain]]ing (from). {{defdate|First attested in the early 17<sup>th</sup> century.}}
# The act of [[declining]] to [[vote]] on a particular issue. {{defdate|First attested in the late 19<sup>th</sup> century.}}
# [[non-participation|Non-participation]] in the [[political]] [[world]]; as a [[country]] avoiding [[international]] [[affairs]].

